libgtksourceviewmm: libgtksourceviewmm (C++ Bindings for GTK Source Code Widgets)
libgtksourceviewmm:
libgtksourceviewmm: Gtksourceview is a text widget that extends the standard gtk+ text
libgtksourceviewmm: widget. It improves GtkTextviewmm by implementing syntax highlighting
libgtksourceviewmm: and other features typical of a source editor.
libgtksourceviewmm:
libgtksourceviewmm: This package offers C++ Bindings for the GTK Source Code Widgets.
